p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: The query will follow relation from the parents of the last level
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92:
Query instances of (Person) follow relation (hasPet) to data type (Pet). If you backtrack your query by one hop, you will be performing follow from (Person) data type again. 
E.g. Query instances of (Person) follow (hasPet) back () follow (hasEmployer).
